# Landing — apps/landing

## Stack

Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, next-intl, next-themes, Tailwind v4, `@repo/ui`.

## Scope

- Marketing/public product pages only.
- Auth pages and OAuth callbacks live in `apps/dashboard`.
- CTA links use `NEXT_PUBLIC_DASHBOARD_URL`.
- Public market data may use a minimal server-side GraphQL fetcher; do not move dashboard entities/query layer into landing.

## i18n

- Use next-intl with `localePrefix: 'never'`.
- Messages come from `@repo/i18n-messages`.

## UI

- Import primitives from `@repo/ui/...`.
- Import shared styles through `@repo/ui/styles.css`.
- shadcn CLI config lives only in `packages/ui/components.json`.
- Next.js keeps `postcss.config.mjs` with `@tailwindcss/postcss` for Tailwind v4.
- Prefer arrow functions for new React components, hooks, and helpers.
- Keep landing-specific composition in `src/widgets`.
